<subSubSection pageId="0" pageNumber="49" type="etymology">
<paragraph pageId="0" pageNumber="49">Etymology.</paragraph>
<paragraph pageId="0" pageNumber="49">The species name refers to the fact that Hawaii, where the holotype of this fungus was collected, is regarded as a paradise by travellers.</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
